Community note text in capture: \"A pregnancy test cannot detect a pregnancy until at least 2 weeks after you have unprotected sex.\" It links to a GoodRx URL via t.co.\n\nWeight note: This is not a statement from Clavicular. It is the viral social post/fan-news claim that later fact checks discussed. It supports that a widely viewed claim of a girlfriend pregnancy circulated during the period; its community note and lack of direct speaker context undermine its weight as proof of a credible Clavicular announcement."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782803753374},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me check the Gamma API evidence to understand the market context:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f812","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_read_evidence_range","args":"{\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e0434e9fb3cb_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-e0434e9fb3cb\",\"offset\":0,\"length\":2492}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":696,"output":77,"cacheRead":57344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782803753376,"responseId":"gen-1782803753-4ffZo1paBEkn5rGLyvfw"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f812","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C4\ncase_id: arb-ex09-20260630065125\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C4\nremaining_ms: 810853\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex09-20260630065125\",\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"content_base64\":\"\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e0434e9fb3cb_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-e0434e9fb3cb\",\"length\":2492,\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"offset\":0,\"remaining_read_bytes_for_opportunity\":517257,\"remaining_reads_for_opportunity\":29,\"sha256\":\"e0434e9fb3cb05b404fd6d6e00816f140fb388fa5d6ea0f6eabbd37bdc0b2580\",\"total_size_bytes\":2492},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3